divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking pics of unusual fingerprint cloud formations. A trail appeared in some light clouds passing above. No noise or airplane in area. Looked back at my pics and found this object in one of them. The trail appeared within 3-5 seconds of me looking around for unusual cloud patterns. Object is in pic #2.
